	<div style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/johncohen/55582632/"><img class="posterous_download_image" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/32/55582632_0ee7885f06.jpg" border="0" height="500" width="375" /></a></div>
